      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "UserAccount — Aggregate Root\n\nEstado\n• id, bancaId, username\n• name, email? (não exclusivo)\n• status, credential\n• mustChangePassword\n• failedAttempts, lockedUntil\n\nInvariante\n• username único dentro da banca\n\nComportamentos\n• changePassword() / forceReset()\n• registerLoginFailure() / unlock()",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "UserAccount — Aggregate Root\n\nEstado\n• id, bancaId, username\n• name, email? (não exclusivo)\n• status, credential\n• mustChangePassword\n• failedAttempts, lockedUntil\n\nInvariante\n• username único dentro da banca\n\nComportamentos\n• changePassword() / forceReset()\n• registerLoginFailure() / unlock()",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
